<h3>Mission Cards</h3>

<div id="mission-table" class="table table-100 table-padding-p5">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Northern Influence</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have at least 1 astronaut in 1/2/3/4 of the red zones, gain 1/2/4/7 points.*@
            1+ in VB, Ausonia, TS, Hellas
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Southern Influence</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have at least 1 astronaut in 1/2/3/4 of the red zones, gain 1/2/4/7 points.*@
            1+ in MS, SS, VM, MT
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Eastern Influence</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have at least 1 astronaut in 1/2/3/4 of the red zones, gain 1/2/4/7 points.*@
            1+ in Hellas, TS, MT, SS
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Western Influence</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have at least 1 astronaut in 1/2/3/4 of the red zones, gain 1/2/4/7 points.*@
            1+ in Ausonia, VB, SM, MS
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">9</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Pockets of Influence</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have at least 1 astronaut in <b>each</b> red zone, gain 9 points.*@
            1+ in <b>each</b>: Ausonia, Hellas, MT, MS
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">9</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Colonization</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have the higheste number of astronauts on Mars (not counting Phobos), gain 9 points.*@
            Most on Mars
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">6</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Strategic Zones</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have the highest number of astronauts in <b>both red zones combined</b>, gain 6 points.*@
            Most in SM + VM
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">7</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Satellite</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have the most astronauts on Phobos, gain 7 points.*@
            Most on Phobos
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Collectioneer</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*For each of your point token sets (1 celerium, 1 sylvanite, and 1 ice), gain 2 points.*@
            Token set = 2
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">8</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Sylvanite Stash</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you hae the most sylvanite point tokens, gain 8 points.*@
            Most Sylvanite tokens
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Good Intel</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*For each zone in which you have at least 1 astronaut (including Phobos), gain 1 point.*@
            Each zone: 1+ = 1 point
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Settlement</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*For each of your astronauts in 1 zone of your choice, gain 1 point.*@
            Pick any zone, X astronauts = X points
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">X</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Eternal Fame</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*For each of your astronauts on the Lost in Space Memorial, gain 2 points.*@
            Lost astronaut = 2
        </div>

        <div class="table-cell tc-p2">9</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-p12">Ice Monopoly</div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-4">
            @*If you have the most ice point tokens, gain 9 points. In case of a tie, the tied players evenly divide the 9 points, rounded down.*@
            Most ice tokens
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

